<sect2 id='gimp-layer-transform-menu' lang='en;de;fr;zh_CN'>
  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Transform</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Transformation</quote></phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Transformer</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">变换</phrase>
  </title>

  <figure>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en'>The Transform submenu of the Layer menu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Transformation</quote></phrase>
      <phrase lang='fr'>Le sous-menu Transformer du menu Calque</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">图层菜单的变换子菜单</phrase>
    </title>

    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject lang="en;de">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/menus-layer-transform.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="fr">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/fr/menus-layer-transform.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="zh_CN">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/zh_CN/menus-layer-transform.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>

  <para lang='en'>
    The Transform submenu of the Layers menu contains operations that
    flip or rotate the active layer of the image. 
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    In diesem Untermenü finden Sie verschiedene Kommandos, um Ebenen zu
    spiegeln und zu drehen.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    Le sous-menu Transformer du menu Calque contient les commandes de 
    retournement et de rotation du calque actif.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    图层菜单的变换子菜单包括翻转或旋转图像活动图层的操作。
  </para>

  <sect3 lang="en;de;fr">
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate submenü</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>
          You can accede to it via 
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Layer</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Transformation</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Untermenü kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>T</accel>ransformation</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang='fr'>
          Vous accédez à ce sous-menu par
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>C</accel>alque</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>T</accel>ransformer</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>

  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en;zh_CN'>Transformation Menuitems</phrase>
      <phrase lang='de'>Der Inhalt des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Conntenu du sous-menu Transformer</phrase>
    </title>
    
    <para lang="de">
      Im Untermenü <guilabel>Transformation</guilabel> stehen Ihnen folgende
      Kommandos zur Verfügung:
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-add" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-flip-horizontal" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-flip-vertical" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-rotate-90" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-rotate-270" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-rotate-180" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-rotate-arbitrary" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-offset" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
